{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And definitely the [NON-ENGLISH] Hitler will have a bloody demise.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's why I went back to December.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But in January sometimes, we went-- I left Debrecen-- I mean Satu Mare, Satmar, and I came to Bihor Diosig with my-- with my family, the Goldbergs.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And again, we had to go through the same thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, a sister, she was asking about her brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, and of course, I, I, I, I told my, my old story that I don-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here we are in Bihor Diosig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From there, we stayed-- we stayed there till-- I stayed there till May sometimes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was like in a-- in a house arrest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a house that was in the-- on the main street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were in business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I knew that when people come in, I shouldn't be in the living room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- I was in the-- in the-- like in house arrest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But around May time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somebody-- this uncle of mine had a-- had a-- OK-- had a business dispute with, with somebody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I snuck in one Friday night-- on the same street, there was a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I snuck in Friday night into the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this, this antagonist of my uncle, he saw a strange face, and he kind of inquired, who is that-- who is that stranger there?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started being afraid that he is going to, to say something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started feeling this-- listening that there-- there is whisperings in the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I decided it's, it's time to get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not safe anymore here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this-- this was sometimes around May 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
